      {
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 4.55,
        "duration": 4.55,
        "text": "In this inspiring story, Mei grows up between two cultures."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 4.55,
        "endTime": 8.727,
        "duration": 4.177,
        "text": "She feels different because of her parents' immigration."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 8.727,
        "endTime": 12.53,
        "duration": 3.804,
        "text": "Mei learns about bicultural identity and belonging."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 12.53,
        "endTime": 15.887,
        "duration": 3.356,
        "text": "She goes from shame to pride in her heritage."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 15.887,
        "endTime": 23.271,
        "duration": 7.384,
        "text": "Through finding community and accepting who she is, Mei learns to embrace her place in the world."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 23.271,
        "endTime": 31.104,
        "duration": 7.833,
        "text": "This story gives a powerful message about identity, belonging, and being a bridge between two worlds."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 31.104,
        "endTime": 37.443,
        "duration": 6.339,
        "text": "Imagine being three years old and knowing you are different from everyone around you."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 37.443,
        "endTime": 42.515,
        "duration": 5.072,
        "text": "Mei stood in her new preschool and looked at all the other children."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 42.515,
        "endTime": 44.006,
        "duration": 1.492,
        "text": "They were all white."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 44.006,
        "endTime": 45.722,
        "duration": 1.715,
        "text": "They all spoke English."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 45.722,
        "endTime": 48.183,
        "duration": 2.461,
        "text": "Mei had dark hair and brown eyes."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 48.183,
        "endTime": 51.241,
        "duration": 3.058,
        "text": "She spoke Cantonese with her grandfather."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 51.241,
        "endTime": 56.537,
        "duration": 5.296,
        "text": "When her grandfather tried to leave that first morning, Mei screamed."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 56.537,
        "endTime": 58.401,
        "duration": 1.865,
        "text": "She threw a terrible fit."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 58.401,
        "endTime": 62.951,
        "duration": 4.55,
        "text": "Because she knew if he left, she would be completely alone."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 62.951,
        "endTime": 64.667,
        "duration": 1.715,
        "text": "Her grandfather stayed."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 64.667,
        "endTime": 69.068,
        "duration": 4.401,
        "text": "Every day for two years, he stayed at preschool with her."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 69.068,
        "endTime": 70.559,
        "duration": 1.492,
        "text": "This is Mei's story."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 70.559,
        "endTime": 73.692,
        "duration": 3.132,
        "text": "It is about growing up between two worlds."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 73.692,
        "endTime": 77.421,
        "duration": 3.729,
        "text": "About feeling shame for the people she loved most."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 77.421,
        "endTime": 80.926,
        "duration": 3.505,
        "text": "About learning that she did not have to choose."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 80.926,
        "endTime": 87.639,
        "duration": 6.712,
        "text": "About discovering that being caught between two cultures could create something beautiful."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 87.639,
        "endTime": 88.683,
        "duration": 1.044,
        "text": "Something new."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 88.683,
        "endTime": 89.354,
        "duration": 0.671,
        "text": "A bridge."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 89.354,
        "endTime": 93.083,
        "duration": 3.729,
        "text": "Many children grow up caught between two cultures."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 93.083,
        "endTime": 95.768,
        "duration": 2.685,
        "text": "Their parents come from one country."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 95.768,
        "endTime": 98.527,
        "duration": 2.759,
        "text": "But the children are born in another."
      },
      {
        "startTime": 98.527,
        "endTime": 102.331,
